<section class="page-title">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h4 class="text-uppercase">심사하기</h4>
                <ol class="breadcrumb">
                    <li>
                        <a>내가올린마켓</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="active">
                        <a>심사하기</a>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<div class = "wrapper">
  <div class = "container">
    <div class="page-content">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="heading-title-alt text-center">
          <h1 class="text-uppercase">Judgement</h1>
          <span class="text-uppercase">공정한 심사로 마켓의 신뢰성을 높여봅시다</span>
        </div>
        <br><br><br>
        <div class = "row col-xs-offset-2 col-xs-8 text-center">
          <div class = "row">
            <div class="heading-title-alt text-center">
              <h4 class="text-uppercase">개인정보확인</h4>
              <span class="text-uppercase">구체적으로 작성했는지 판단해 보세요</span>
            </div>
            <div class = "col-xs-offset-4 col-xs-4 text-center">
              <input class = "form-control text-center" onblur="findTotal()" type="number" name="qty" id="qty2" min = "0" max = "10"/><br>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class = "row">
            <div class="heading-title-alt text-center">
              <h4 class="text-uppercase">경력확인</h4>
              <span class="text-uppercase">경력이 있을경우 가산점을 주실 수 있습니다.</span>
            </div>
            <div class = "col-xs-offset-4 col-xs-4 text-center">
              <input class = "form-control text-center" onblur="findTotal()" type="number" name="qty" id="qty3" min="0" max = "10"/><br>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class = "row">
            <div class="heading-title-alt text-center">
              <h4 class="text-uppercase">참여 아이템 적합성</h4>
              <span class="text-uppercase">아이템의 제작과정을 열람하고 심사하실 수 있습니다.</span>
            </div>
            <div class = "col-xs-offset-4 col-xs-4 text-center">
              <input class = "form-control text-center" onblur="findTotal()" type="number" name="qty" id="qty4" min="0" max = "10"/><br>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class = "row">
            <div class="heading-title-alt text-center">
              <h4 class="text-uppercase">심사총평</h4>
              <span class="text-uppercase"></span>
            </div>
            <textarea class="form-control" name = "content" rows="10" id="emailcontent"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="divider divider-small d-solid d-single text-center">
              <span class="dot"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="heading-title-alt text-center">
            <h4 class="text-uppercase">총점</h4>
          </div>
          <input class = "form-control" type="number" name="total" id="total"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
function findTotal(){
    var arr = document.getElementsByName('qty');
    var tot=0;
    for(var i=0;i<arr.length;i++){
        if(parseInt(arr[i].value))
            tot += parseInt(arr[i].value);
    }
    document.getElementById('total').value = tot;
}
</script>
